USAGE

  fez dep <dist> [-b] [-t]

  fez depends <dist> [--build=False] [--test=False]

FLAGS

  OPTIONAL

  -b|--build          adds the <dist> to build depends rather than
                      runtime depends
  -t|--test           adds the <dist> to test depends rather than
                      runtime depends

Adds a dependency to the META file.
